- [x] I have added necessary documentation (if appropriate)
- [ x] It's small enought so they can be easily reviewed.
- [ x] I have CONSIDERED or ADDED a unit test if the PR resolves an issue.

### Does this introduce a breaking change?

- [ x] No

<!-- If this introduces a breaking change, please describe the impact and migration path for existing applications below. -->

This is a pull request for GSOC 2021 sign language project. Adding 3 interface files for these components.
